    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy.stats import gaussian_kde\n",
    "\n",
    "# Function for reading and processing data\n",
    "def read_and_process_data(filename):\n",
    "    df = pd.read_csv(filename, sep='\\t')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Convert infinities to NaN\n",
    "    df.replace([np.inf, -np.inf], np.nan, inplace=True)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    df = df.iloc[::100]\n",
    "    x = df['re'] * 10\n",
    "    y = df['rg'] * 10\n",
    "    firstframex = df['re'].iloc[0] * 10\n",
    "    firstframey = df['rg'].iloc[0] * 10\n",
    "    return x, y, firstframex, firstframey\n",
    "\n",
    "# Reading and processing of the data for each file\n",
    "files = ['re_vs_rg_aa_2us.xvg', 're_vs_rg_aa_2us_neutral.xvg', 'dist_vs_rog_AF.dat', 'dist_vs_rog_AFex.dat']\n",
    "data = [read_and_process_data(file) for file in files]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Creation of the 2x2 multiplot\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(7, 4.5))\n",
    "#sns.set_style(\"whitegrid\")\n",
    "\n",
    "for ax, (x, y, firstframex, firstframey) in zip(axes.ravel(), data):\n",
    "    sns.set_style(\"whitegrid\")\n",
    "    kde = sns.kdeplot(x=x, y=y, cmap='Spectral', fill=True, thresh=0.25, n_levels=10, bw_adjust=1, ax=ax)\n",
    "    ax.scatter(46.191, 24.118, s=50, marker='*', color='black')\n",
    "    ax.set_xlim(15, 75)\n",
    "    ax.set_ylim(20, 26)\n",
    "    ax.set_xlabel('Re ($\\AA$)')\n",
    "    ax.set_ylabel('Rg ($\\AA$)')\n",
    "    cb = plt.colorbar(kde.collections[0], ax=ax)\n",
    "    cb.set_label('Energy (kcal/mol)')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Normalization of the energy values in kcal/mol\n",
    "    kb = 8.617333262145e-5\n",
    "    T = 300\n",
    "    ticks = cb.get_ticks()\n",
    "    energy_ticks = [-kb * T * np.log(p) * 23.06054 for p in ticks]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Linear normalization to a range of 0 to 10\n",
    "    normalized_energy_ticks = [(energy - min(energy_ticks)) / (max(energy_ticks) - min(energy_ticks)) * 10 for energy in energy_ticks]\n",
    "    cb.set_label('Energy (kcal/mol)', rotation=270, labelpad=15)  \n",
    "    cb.ax.yaxis.set_ticks_position('right')\n",
    "    cb.ax.invert_yaxis()\n",
    "    cb.set_ticks(ticks[::-1])\n",
    "    cb.set_ticklabels([f'{energy:.2f}' for energy in normalized_energy_ticks[::-1]])\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "#plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "fig.savefig(\"FEL_AA_all.png\", format='png', dpi=350, transparent=False)\n",
    "fig.savefig(\"FEL_AA_all.svg\", format='svg', dpi=350, transparent=False)"
